        "subject": "LU-4730 utils: more lctl get_param, set_param cleanups",
        "message": "LU-4730 utils: more lctl get_param, set_param cleanups\n\nEnsure there is enough space in parameter printing when using \"-F\".\nPrint a trailing '?' for parameters on which lstat() fails.\n\nReturn an error for parameters with full or embedded relative\npaths to avoid strangeness.\n\nCode style cleanups.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I1004b5b4da4dc9b5825ef498758e248ed5500c1e\n"
      },
